[ Upstream commit fd0b5ba87ad5709f0fd3d2bc4b7870494a75f96a ]

Set .flags = CLK_OPS_PARENT_ENABLE to fix "gcc_sdcc2_apps_clk_src: rcg
didn't update its configuration" error.

